


     DeletePort(31.0)	  ARP Programmers Manual      DeletePort(31.0)



     NAME
	  DeletePort - Deletes a message port.

     SYNOPSIS
	  DeletePort(port)
		      A1

     FUNCTION
	  Removes a message port.

     INPUTS
	  port - pointer to a message port may be private or public.
		  You may safely pass this function a NULL pointer.

     RESULT
	  The message port, signals, and associated memory are
	  released.  Nothing is	returned.

     BUGS
	  None known.

     SEE ALSO
	  CreatePort

     AUTHOR
	  SDB





























